02:17:10.320 --> 02:17:17.280
I would call Cold War America. And the taboo in Cold War America, running from around 1945-6

02:17:18.160 --> 02:17:28.320
to the present, I mean really never stopped, was a Manichaean worldview. The United States is good,

02:17:28.320 --> 02:17:33.760
it defines democracy, and the Soviet Union is awful, it defines whatever the opposite

02:17:33.760 --> 02:17:44.160
