02:17:44.720 --> 02:17:53.280
of academic individuals, it was impossible to talk, have a conversation. I mean,

02:17:54.000 --> 02:17:59.920
I can't tell, just make it very personal. The number of times I would raise my hand in my classes

02:17:59.920 --> 02:18:08.720
at Harvard or Stanford or Yale, and I would ask a question that had something to do with Marxism,

02:18:08.720 --> 02:18:14.240
