02:20:03.840 --> 02:20:08.960
and the system will collapse. You need the government to come in to solve the problems,

02:20:08.960 --> 02:20:14.080
to fix the weaknesses. And they hate each other, and they throw each other out of their jobs.

02:20:14.720 --> 02:20:19.600
One of the very few things they can do together that they agree on is keeping people like me out.

02:20:21.200 --> 02:20:27.760
That they can find common ground to do. So I had to learn it all on my own.

02:20:27.760 --> 02:20:37.360
Why am I telling you this? Because this taboo means that all of the complicated developments

